metadata.name: Rosetta
metadata.description:
She is the captain of the VOIDs special forces unit, RUNAWAYS. She is the younger sister of Lucille, the general commander.  She can make her body and anything she touches invisible. While invisible, she can slip through walls and is virtually invincible against physical attacks, but she cannot remain invisible for long due to the high energy consumption. It is said that while she is using her ability, it is similar to running as fast as she can. She is often scolded for calling Lucille "sis" during missions and told to call her "commander".

VOIDs特殊部隊、RUNAWAYSの隊長。総隊長ルシールの妹。彼女の能力は透明化。自分の体、そして触れている物を透明にする事が出来る。透明になっている間は壁をすり抜けることもでき、物理攻撃には実質無敵だが、体力の消費が激しいために長くは透明でいられない。感覚的に能力を使用している間は全力の疾走に近いらしい。任務中にルシールの事をお姉ちゃんと呼んでは、総隊長と呼びなさい、とよく叱られている。
